      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市因中东风险和美国数据而波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待美国价格数据来指导美联储的政策路径，同时中东紧张局势加剧打压了风险偏好，欧洲股市走势艰难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 22:48:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉下调以色列评级，称战争可能持续至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/israel-s-rating-cut-by-fitch-as-gaza-war-seen-lasting-into-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级将以色列的主权债务评级下调了一个等级，并维持对以色列信用状况的负面展望，因为持续的军事冲突对该国的公共财政造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/israel-s-rating-cut-by-fitch-as-gaza-war-seen-lasting-into-2025</guid>
